{"about_the_game":"<strong>BUILD YOUR OWN DREAM SKYSCRAPER</strong><br><br>In &quot;Mad Tower Tycoon&quot; you can build your own skyscraper with more than 100 floors.<br>The classic construction gameplay leaves you all the freedom.<br>Rent offices, apartments or shops and build a financially lucrative skyscraper.<br>Build restaurants, cinemas, zoos or underground garages to satisfy your visitors.<br>There are countless ways to get the coveted &quot;six-star award&quot; for your skyscraper.<br><br><br><strong>REALISTIC ELEVATORS</strong><br>The waiting time should be increased? It should be avoided some floors?<br>No problem: the elevator system in &quot;Mad Tower Tycoon&quot; allows you different settings.<br>Avoid your visitors having to climb too many stairs or wait too long for the elevator.<br><br><strong>RANDOM EVENTS</strong><br>Not only dissatisfied tenants are causing you trouble.<br>A fire in the new office, an earthquake shakes your skyscraper or UFOs kidnap your tenants.<br>Different events provide variety and excitement.<br><br><strong>LEVEL SYSTEM</strong><br>Complete daily missions and have good statistics to gain experience.<br>Earn skill points and unlock more than 50 skills.<br><br><strong>DETAILED STATISTICS</strong><br>You want to see which floors are dirty or where the noise is unbearable?<br>How many visitors came in the last 24 hours? Have I made a higher profit in the last 30 days?<br>The statistics and filters in &quot;Mad Tower Tycoon&quot; will give you a lot of information about the state of your skyscraper.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The First Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/910880/47c0a6cc8101607333022e4aae0d1fd3338e41e5.jpg"},{"name":"The Second Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/910880/f47d542f15a0c1923f254020d9b72bb9e2887957.jpg"},{"name":"The Third Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima